OL,3,CPolice appeal for witnesses after man
OL,4,Cleft with with 'serious head injury'
OL,6,FPolice officers investigating a report
OL,7,Fof a serious assault in Abertillery
OL,8,Fare appealing for witnesses.
OL,10,FAt around midnight on Monday, 4 May,
OL,11,FGwent Police received a report that a
OL,12,Fman had sustained a serious head
OL,13,Finjury following an assault in an
OL,14,Falleyway off Division Street.
OL,16,FA 60-year-old man was taken to
OL,17,Fhospital for his injuries. They are
OL,18,Fnot thought to be life-threatening.
OL,20,FEnquiries are ongoing to establish the
OL,21,Fcircumstances.
