OL,3,CPolice appeal for witnesses after man
OL,4,Cleft with with 'serious head injury'
OL,6,FGwent Police are now appealing for
OL,7,Fanyone who was in the area between
OL,8,F11.30pm on Sunday, 3 May and 12.30am
OL,9,Fon Monday, 4 May, or anyone who may
OL,10,Fhave information useful to the
OL,11,Finvestigation to get in contact.
